  17:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / Feb 26,'06 R0.00  Prototype.
  18:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /
  19:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / Apr 29,'06 R0.01  First stable version.
  20:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /
  21:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / Jun 01,'06 R0.02  Added FAT12 support.
  22:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Removed unbuffered mode.
  23:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed a problem on small (<32M) partition.
  24:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / Jun 10,'06 R0.02a Added a configuration option (_FS_MINIMUM).
  25:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /
  26:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / Sep 22,'06 R0.03  Added f_rename().
  27:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Changed option _FS_MINIMUM to _FS_MINIMIZE.
  28:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / Dec 11,'06 R0.03a Improved cluster scan algorithm to write files fast.
  29:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed f_mkdir() creates incorrect directory on FAT32.
ARM GAS  C:\Users\Xuleo\AppData\Local\Temp\ccLX7nbq.s 			page 2


  30:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /
  31:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / Feb 04,'07 R0.04  Supported multiple drive system.
  32:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Changed some interfaces for multiple drive system.
  33:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Changed f_mountdrv() to f_mount().
  34:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Added f_mkfs().
  35:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / Apr 01,'07 R0.04a Supported multiple partitions on a physical drive.
  36:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Added a capability of extending file size to f_lseek().
  37:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Added minimization level 3.
  38:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed an endian sensitive code in f_mkfs().
  39:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / May 05,'07 R0.04b Added a configuration option _USE_NTFLAG.
  40:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Added FSINFO support.
  41:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed DBCS name can result FR_INVALID_NAME.
  42:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed short seek (<= csize) collapses the file object.
  43:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /
  44:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / Aug 25,'07 R0.05  Changed arguments of f_read(), f_write() and f_mkfs().
  45:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed f_mkfs() on FAT32 creates incorrect FSINFO.
  46:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed f_mkdir() on FAT32 creates incorrect directory.
  47:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / Feb 03,'08 R0.05a Added f_truncate() and f_utime().
  48:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed off by one error at FAT sub-type determination.
  49:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed btr in f_read() can be mistruncated.
  50:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed cached sector is not flushed when create and close without write.
  51:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /
  52:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / Apr 01,'08 R0.06  Added fputc(), fputs(), fprintf() and fgets().
  53:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Improved performance of f_lseek() on moving to the same or following cluster.
  54:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /
  55:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / Apr 01,'09 R0.07  Merged Tiny-FatFs as a configuration option. (_FS_TINY)
  56:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Added long file name feature.
  57:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Added multiple code page feature.
  58:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Added re-entrancy for multitask operation.
  59:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Added auto cluster size selection to f_mkfs().
  60:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Added rewind option to f_readdir().
  61:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Changed result code of critical errors.
  62:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Renamed string functions to avoid name collision.
  63:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / Apr 14,'09 R0.07a Separated out OS dependent code on reentrant cfg.
  64:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Added multiple sector size feature.
  65:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / Jun 21,'09 R0.07c Fixed f_unlink() can return FR_OK on error.
  66:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed wrong cache control in f_lseek().
  67:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Added relative path feature.
  68:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Added f_chdir() and f_chdrive().
  69:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Added proper case conversion to extended character.
  70:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / Nov 03,'09 R0.07e Separated out configuration options from ff.h to ffconf.h.
  71:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed f_unlink() fails to remove a sub-directory on _FS_RPATH.
  72:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed name matching error on the 13 character boundary.
  73:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Added a configuration option, _LFN_UNICODE.
  74:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Changed f_readdir() to return the SFN with always upper case on non-LFN cfg.
  75:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /
  76:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / May 15,'10 R0.08  Added a memory configuration option. (_USE_LFN = 3)
  77:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Added file lock feature. (_FS_SHARE)
  78:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Added fast seek feature. (_USE_FASTSEEK)
  79:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Changed some types on the API, XCHAR->TCHAR.
  80:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Changed .fname in the FILINFO structure on Unicode cfg.
  81:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   String functions support UTF-8 encoding files on Unicode cfg.
  82:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / Aug 16,'10 R0.08a Added f_getcwd().
  83:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Added sector erase feature. (_USE_ERASE)
  84:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Moved file lock semaphore table from fs object to the bss.
  85:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed a wrong directory entry is created on non-LFN cfg when the given name con
  86:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed f_mkfs() creates wrong FAT32 volume.
ARM GAS  C:\Users\Xuleo\AppData\Local\Temp\ccLX7nbq.s 			page 3


  87:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / Jan 15,'11 R0.08b Fast seek feature is also applied to f_read() and f_write().
  88:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   f_lseek() reports required table size on creating CLMP.
  89:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Extended format syntax of f_printf().
  90:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Ignores duplicated directory separators in given path name.
  91:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /
  92:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / Sep 06,'11 R0.09  f_mkfs() supports multiple partition to complete the multiple partition feature
  93:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Added f_fdisk().
  94:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / Aug 27,'12 R0.09a Changed f_open() and f_opendir() reject null object pointer to avoid crash.
  95:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Changed option name _FS_SHARE to _FS_LOCK.
  96:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed assertion failure due to OS/2 EA on FAT12/16 volume.
  97:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / Jan 24,'13 R0.09b Added f_setlabel() and f_getlabel().
  98:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /
  99:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / Oct 02,'13 R0.10  Added selection of character encoding on the file. (_STRF_ENCODE)
 100:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Added f_closedir().
 101:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Added forced full FAT scan for f_getfree(). (_FS_NOFSINFO)
 102:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Added forced mount feature with changes of f_mount().
 103:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Improved behavior of volume auto detection.
 104:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Improved write throughput of f_puts() and f_printf().
 105:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Changed argument of f_chdrive(), f_mkfs(), disk_read() and disk_write().
 106:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed f_write() can be truncated when the file size is close to 4GB.
 107:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed f_open(), f_mkdir() and f_setlabel() can return incorrect error code.
 108:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / Jan 15,'14 R0.10a Added arbitrary strings as drive number in the path name. (_STR_VOLUME_ID)
 109:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Added a configuration option of minimum sector size. (_MIN_SS)
 110:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   2nd argument of f_rename() can have a drive number and it will be ignored.
 111:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed f_mount() with forced mount fails when drive number is >= 1.
 112:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed f_close() invalidates the file object without volume lock.
 113:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed f_closedir() returns but the volume lock is left acquired.
 114:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed creation of an entry with LFN fails on too many SFN collisions.
 115:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / May 19,'14 R0.10b Fixed a hard error in the disk I/O layer can collapse the directory entry.
 116:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed LFN entry is not deleted on delete/rename an object with lossy converted 
 117:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / Nov  9,'14 R0.10c Added a configuration option for the platforms without RTC. (_FS_NORTC)
 118:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed volume label created by Mac OS X cannot be retrieved with f_getlabel(). (
 119:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed a potential problem of FAT access that can appear on disk error.
 120:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed null pointer dereference on attempting to delete the root direcotry. (app
 121:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** / Feb 02,'15 R0.11  Added f_findfirst() and f_findnext(). (_USE_FIND)
 122:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed f_unlink() does not remove cluster chain of the file. (appeared at R0.10c
 123:./ThirdParty/FatFs/ff.c **** /                   Fixed _FS_NORTC option does not work properly. (appeared at R0.10c)
